                              and <persName>Ignatius</persName> are traced in rude Greek
                                 letters,<foreign xml:lang="grc">ⲤⲈⲎⲢⲈ ⲎⲄⲚⲀⲦⲎⲞⲤ</foreign>. </p>
                           <p>
                    <quote xml:lang="syr"/>
                  </p>
                        </item>
